OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772447794
OL,3,CDubai's Fairmont The Palm Hotel hit as
OL,4,CIranian retaliatory strikes continue
OL,6,FDubai's famous Fairmont The Palm Hotel
OL,7,Fhas been hit following retaliatory
OL,8,Fstrikes by Iran.
OL,10,FFour people were injured in the fire
OL,11,Fin the Palm Jumeirah area which has
OL,12,Fnow been brought under control, Dubai
OL,13,Fauthorities said.
OL,15,FIran has launched a number of
OL,16,Fcounterattacks against the US and
OL,17,FIsrael following what President Trump
OL,18,Fhas called "major combat operations"
OL,19,Fin the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
