OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772447794
OL,3,CDubai's Fairmont The Palm Hotel hit as
OL,4,CIranian retaliatory strikes continue
OL,6,FIran has fired drones and missiles at
OL,7,FIsrael and strikes aimed at US
OL,8,Fmilitary installations in Bahrain,
OL,9,FKuwait and Qatar.
OL,11,FSaudi Arabia said on state-run media
OL,12,Fthat it had repelled attacks by Iran
OL,13,Fon its capital and eastern region, and
OL,14,Fsirens sounded in Jordan.
OL,16,FAn apartment building in northern
OL,17,FIsrael was damaged and shrapnel fell
OL,18,Fin multiple sites, according to media
OL,19,Fand police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
