OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772447794
OL,3,CDubai's Fairmont The Palm Hotel hit as
OL,4,CIranian retaliatory strikes continue
OL,6,FAbout 12 hours after the attacks
OL,7,Fbegan, the US military reported no US
OL,8,Fcasualties and minimal damage at its
OL,9,Fbases despite "hundreds of Iranian
OL,10,Fmissile and drone attacks."
OL,12,FIsrael's military say that that
OL,13,F"dozens" of missiles have been fired
OL,14,Fby Iran at Israel.
OL,16,FWhile many have been intercepted and
OL,17,Fno serious injuries have been
OL,18,Freported, the missile barrages were
OL,19,Fcontinuing after sundown on Saturday.
