OL,4,CIranian retaliatory strikes continue
OL,6,FIsrael's military chief gave an
OL,7,Faddress on national TV warning that
OL,8,Fthe defences are not "hermetic" and
OL,9,Fthe public should obey safety
OL,10,Finstructions and remain vigilant.
